{"tid":343110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女子遭壓路機輾斃 屍體毀滅性粉碎","createTime":"2017-08-01T07:32:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T09:16:09.000Z","uid":70786,"like":86,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f4a7bdbf059770edc6225c07d0facac14afaa6d8","tid":343110,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T07:32:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YGpB85EtF1I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYGpB85EtF1I&d=7u%2FeXx4%2FGDu%2FYNzLwCZNfhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=8c79e027\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YGpB85EtF1I</a><br />\n<br />\n 黑龍江發生一起恐怖意外，一輛在路上的壓路機將一名女子輾壓死亡，情境恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n據「生命警示錄」微信指出，事發於上周五(7月28日)，黑龍江富錦市市場監督管理局門前，一輛壓路機將一名途人壓倒。有指死者為一名女性。據網上流傳的照片所見，壓路機駛開後，死者遺體遭完全輾碎，情境恐怖震撼。惟事故原因尚未釐清。目前尚不知道事故原因。"},{"pid":"a9969fe6b717a64246ab37a2885e824e72c11ceb","tid":343110,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T07:33:24.000Z","msg":"渣都冇? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b24de7abe47aae930e8c1786f284c0d25c0adead","tid":343110,"uid":70786,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T07:35:00.000Z","msg":"步兵:<a href=\"https://www.liveleak.com/view?i=e1e_1501304279\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.liveleak.com%2Fview%3Fi%3De1e_1501304279&d=7u%2FeXx4%2FGDu%2FYNzLwCZNfhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=ba700870\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.liveleak.com/view?i=e1e_1501304279</a>"},{"pid":"175a21834faa626b7d710181f7f7e9de2add551c","tid":343110,"uid":8497,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T07:35:10.000Z","msg":"想知條片有咩意義"},{"pid":"42882e0430bcb371263632356ff3cd7543c816a6","tid":343110,"uid":70786,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T07:36:22.000Z","msg":"壓路機真係好難避，好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.yout